					"contents": [
						{
							"type": "text",
							"params": "<div><blockquote><p>Clotho is a software environment for authoring and sharing the tools and data needed to perform a synthetic biology project. This tutorial will guide you through the basics of genetic design and Clotho usage.</p></blockquote><p>Videos like this will help you get up to speed. This one will give you a brief introduction to DNA and Synthetic Biology. <b>Feel free to <a ng-click=\"next()\">skip ahead</a> if this isn't new to you.</b></p></div>"
